        "gg3BajX3jAe_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">This is the most important part. I learned that mouth breathing actually keeps your body in a state of stress (\"fight or flight\") all night, preventing you from fully shutting down. By forcing nasal breathing,<strong> this tape increases oxygen intake and signals your nervous system to relax.</strong> It pushes you into deep REM sleep much faster. I’m not just waking up less groggy<strong>; I’m waking up with lower cortisol levels and actual energy. This is where the real body repair and \"beauty sleep\" happens.</strong></span></p>",
        "ggHIzq54zz__text": "5. It Doesn't Hurt To Take Off",
        "ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/7_9_d8488d5d-47eb-4661-abe7-7bc8e3459cd9.png",
        "ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/7_9.png",
        "ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/7_9.png",
        "ggL99cbnlZo_text": "<p><strong>UPDATE:</strong> The Collagen Mouth Tape is currently in stock, but inventory is moving fast. Check the link below to see if it's available.</p>",
        "ggMTtLiPXuX_text": "<p>By Eleanor Brooks | London, UK<br>December 7, 2025</p>",
        "ggNzvrSfCrV_text": "2. It’s Collagen Skincare, Not Just Tape",
        "ggOGc25WEdF_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">It’s always annoying to buy a new product and hate it.&nbsp;<strong>Nifora offers a risk-free trial, so if you find it uncomfortable or don't see a difference, you aren't stuck with it</strong>. For me, the better sleep and smoother skin are worth it.</span></p>",
        "ggOkzpODfF8_text": "6. The Quality of My Sleep Has Completely Changed",
        "ggQ78Sg6Zrx_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">My biggest worry was that it would hurt to peel off in the morning. Because of the collagen infusion,&nbsp;<strong>the adhesive is actually very gentle</strong>. It stays on all night without issues, but in the morning,&nbsp;<strong>it peels off easily without pulling my skin or leaving red marks.</strong></span></p>",
        "ggQPtwZzMvG_text": "4. It’s The Ultimate 3-in-1 Multitasker&nbsp;",
        "ggTCZJLSmNN_text": "7. You Can Try It Risk-Free",
        "ggUMmUh3HgV_label": "<p>CHECK AVAILABILITY</p>",
        "ggUYRw8nmHu_text": "Discover why 40,000+ women using Collagen Infused Mouth Tape &nbsp;To Snatch Their Jawline and Hydrate Lips While They Sleep",
        "ggUrpHf4v9e_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(244,204,204,0);color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">Experts have found that mouth breathing keeps your body in a&nbsp;<strong>state of micro-stress (Fight or Flight)</strong> all night long. This spikes your Cortisol levels, which causes your body to hold onto water, leading to that round \"Moon Face\" look in the morning.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(244,204,204,0);color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">Nifora forces your body to switch into deep restorative&nbsp;<strong>Nasal Breathing</strong>. This allows your body to naturally drain excess fluid and inflammation while you sleep. The result?&nbsp;<strong>You wake up with a slim, depuffed face and defined cheekbones</strong>, without needing to ice roll for 20 minutes.</span></p>",
        "ggWic5B8SZG_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/2_363a1120-58ca-4eb3-aa4f-e5c1111099f5.png",
        "ggWic5B8SZG_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/2_363a1120-58ca-4eb3-aa4f-e5c1111099f5.png",
        "ggWic5B8SZG_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/14_3ba448f7-4a84-46d3-af45-6033c186a8bb.png",
        "ggYy6grbLeA_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/8_5_23f4496c-434f-4f47-bb12-c6ce8f7eab62.png",
        "ggYy6grbLeA_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/8_5.png",
        "ggYy6grbLeA_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/8_5.png",
        "ggZHuYgoc8x_text": "1. It’s A \"Nighttime Retainer\" For Your Face Structure.",
        "ggfwG-WQa7r_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">That’s when I found this brand, unlike harsh medical tapes, they created a&nbsp;<strong>Hydrolyzed Collagen&nbsp;</strong>version that actively hydrates your skin while you wear it.&nbsp;</span><br><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">I’m usually skeptical of viral products, but I decided to put this to the test for a week.</span></p>",
        "gggTy2IY0Ux_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/banner.png",
        "gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/3_af5c6679-5f2e-4bbf-a39e-37c62d3d42ca.png",
        "gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/6_8.png",
        "gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/6_8.png",
        "ggj-_y-Y_PO_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/6_8_bfecaf0b-d088-4b11-aa79-fb3a06b98d45.png",
        "ggj-_y-Y_PO_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/5_10.png",
        "ggj-_y-Y_PO_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/5_10.png",
        "ggj-b7-Ufnz_text": "Here are the 7 reasons why I’ve actually stuck with it:",
        "ggjPk9bJpvM_text": "3. It Lowers \"Cortisol Face\" (Morning Puffiness)",
        "ggjpl9EZF7-_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/d0af24a7-5b52-4e74-b870-e93a5ce17581.jpg",
        "ggjpl9EZF7-_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/d0af24a7-5b52-4e74-b870-e93a5ce17581.jpg",
        "ggjpl9EZF7-_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/d0af24a7-5b52-4e74-b870-e93a5ce17581.jpg",
        "ggl71u75c7R_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/14_f80008c3-2301-4dd6-8cc9-ec0fc76f212e.png",
        "ggl71u75c7R_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/14_f80008c3-2301-4dd6-8cc9-ec0fc76f212e.png",
        "ggl71u75c7R_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/15_010c2149-8447-41b5-ae4e-398283c40a19.png",
        "gglV0yKrbqN_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/2_Image_8b826f48-8717-401c-98a8-c57b63404528.png",
        "gglV0yKrbqN_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/3_12.png",
        "gglV0yKrbqN_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/3_12.png",
        "ggsdxtqBRbP_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/1_12_50193272-513c-40d6-8a84-526e705d46b1.png",
        "gguCnwVa854_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Frame_1484580952_80c40562-ca10-49d4-9ebc-102373a42a14.png",
        "ggvDN5djePx_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(244, 204, 204, 0);color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">When your mouth hangs open at night, gravity drags your facial muscles downward for 8 hours straight. This creates what experts call&nbsp;<strong>\"Mouth Breather Face\"</strong>: a longer, droopier face shape.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(244, 204, 204, 0);color:#000000;font-size:16px;\"><strong>Nifora&nbsp;</strong>prevents this by keeping the jaw lifted and closed. This forces Nasal Breathing, which&nbsp;<strong>naturally rests your tongue on the roof of your mouth (a technique called \"Mewing\")</strong>. The result?&nbsp;<strong>High cheekbones and a snatched jawline, all achieved while you sleep.</strong></span></p>",
        "ggxK_8Xcm8n_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/3_12_b65cbac6-715c-4fbe-be45-a1e02a8fda2c.png",
        "ggxK_8Xcm8n_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/2_Image_8b826f48-8717-401c-98a8-c57b63404528.png",
        "ggxK_8Xcm8n_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/4_13.png",
        "ggxpEEAWkOo_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">I realized this isn't just a sleep aid;<strong> it’s doing three jobs at once</strong>. First, my jawline is getting visible again!&nbsp;<strong>It improves my face posture by keeping my jaw in the right position all night.&nbsp;</strong>Second, while it’s holding that structure,&nbsp;<strong>the collagen is actively treating my skin</strong>. And third, because I’m finally getting deep, restorative sleep,<strong> I wake up feeling genuinely healthy and energized</strong>. It’s rare to find one product that tackles posture, skincare, and health simultaneously.</span></p>",
        "ggxwUzin72S_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">Most mouth tapes are just sticky plastic or paper that can irritate your skin.&nbsp;<strong>Nifora’s strips are infused with Hydrolyzed Collagen</strong>, meaning the particles are small enough to actually sink in while you sleep.&nbsp;<strong>It works like a targeted sheet mask that hydrates the area for 8 hours straight.&nbsp;</strong>So instead of just holding my mouth shut, I’m waking up with that delicate skin feeling softer and plumper.</span></p>",
        "ggy5Uy9f896_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">I’ll be honest—I used to scroll right past the mouth taping trend. It looked uncomfortable. But then I realized it’s actually a&nbsp;<strong>3-in-1 powerhouse: it fixes your sleep, sharpens your jawline, and prevents lip wrinkles all at once.</strong></span></p>"
      },
